data.description:
Welcome to this charming 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home nestled in a family-friendly neighborhood with an array of amenities for children. This spacious and well-maintained house boasts a comfortable layout, perfect for both relaxation and entertainment. The kitchen is equipped with modern appliances and opens to a bright living area with ample natural light. Upstairs, you'll find the generously sized bedrooms, offering plenty of space for expanding. Outside, the community offers covered playgrounds and a refreshing splash pad, providing endless opportunities for outdoor fun and making this property the ideal place for a family to call home. Don't miss the chance to experience the convenience and comfort of this wonderful lease opportunity.
